"}','brochure-ngolo-cultivation-technology_2019-07-30_10:03:04',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>A brochure containing information about the Ngolo or Matengo pit system. This is essentially\\r\\na soil and water conservation system as\\r\\nwell as a fertility restoration technique,\\r\\nthrough refuse decomposition and crop\\r\\nyield enhancement.<\\/p><p>The brochure recommends the system for farmers in  Maseki, Nzauni and\\r\\nMusengo hilly areas.<\\/p><p>It contains some information about the background and advantages of the system, as well as practical advice for implementing it. <\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/p><div class=\\\"page\\\" title=\\\"Page 2\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"layoutArea\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"column\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>Compiled by Centre for Training &amp; Integrated Research\\r\\nfor ASALs Development (CETRAD) Ngolo tea.\\r\\n<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Note: This resource was added to this database as part of a migration of\\r\\n resources from the now defunct CCRP Sphaera platform, and is still \\r\\nawaiting a comprehensive review and quality check. <\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n<p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n<\\/p>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/e5eca706cbb8805c300fb1393165aa23.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=1&ved=2ahUKEwiQpOWA5KfkAhXIbFAKHXLeBYYQFjAAegQIAhAC&url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cetrad.org%2Findex.php%3Foption%3Dcom_docman%26task%3Ddoc_download%26gid%3D11%26Itemid%3D257&usg=AOvVaw1MofapcxLdS30Gs8nDE1LS\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-07-30 10:03:05','2019-10-23 14:49:55',NULL,NULL,'files/brochure-ngolo-cultivation-technology_2019-07-30_10:03:04/brochure-ngolo-cultivation-technology_2019-07-30_10:03:04.zip',1),(331,'{\"en\":\"Fish Bean (Tephrosia vogelii) - Echo Plant Information Sheet\"}','fish-bean-tephrosia-vogelii-echo-plant-informa