articipation des organisations suivantes: AMSP, AOPP, CIRAD, COPROSEM, ICRISAT, IER Institut d\'Econmie Rurale, INERA, UGCPA, Union Locale des producteurs de Cereales de Dioila.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Cette ressource a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 ajout\\u00e9e \\u00e0 cette base de donn\\u00e9es dans le cadre d\'une migration de ressource \\u00e0 partir de la plate-forme CCRP Sphaera, aujourd\'hui disparue, et attend toujours un examen complet et un contr\\u00f4le de la qualit\\u00e9.<br><br><\\/p>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/f62d4447ebbe16627b14d33f869b9228.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[{\\\"path\\\":\\\"files\\\\/presentation-definitions-and-objectives-of-participatory-selection_2019-07-31_09:09:37\\\\/2019-07-31_09:09:37_definitions-et-objectifs-selection-participative.pdf\\\",\\\"storedName\\\":\\\"2019-07-31_09:09:37_definitions-et-objectifs-selection-participative.pdf\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"de\\\\u0301finitions_et_objectifs_se\\\\u0301lection_participative.pdf\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"pdf\\\",\\\"size\\\":821103,\\\"type_id\\\":1}]\"}','{\"en\": null}',NULL,'2017-12-01','2019-07-31 09:09:37','2019-10-23 14:55:06',NULL,NULL,'files/presentation-definitions-and-objectives-of-participatory-selection_2019-07-31_09:09:37/presentation-definitions-and-objectives-of-participatory-selection_2019-07-31_09:09:37.zip',1),(354,'{\"en\":\"Se\\u0301lection participative des varie\\u0301te\\u0301s de sorgho a\\u0300 l\\u2019aide d\\u2019essais multilocaux dans deux zones cibles\"}','selection-participative-des-varietes-de-sorgho-a-laide-dessais-multilocaux-dans-deux-zones-cibles_2019-07-31_09:20:24',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<div class=\\\"page\\\" title=\\\"Page 1\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"layoutArea\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"column\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Re\\u0301sume\\u0301\\r\\n<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>La re\\u0301alisation de progre\\u0300s ge\\u0301ne\\u0301tiques en se\\u0301lection sorgho pour Afrique de l\\u2019Ouest ne\\u0301cessite\\r\\nune adaptation spe\\u0301cifique a\\u0300 chaque zone agroclimatique. L\\u2019e\\u0301valuation multilocale du\\r\\nrendement n\\u2019est pas facile a\\u0300 re\\u0301aliser sur les quelques stations de recherche disponibles\\r\\ndans chaque zone. L\\u2019e\\u0301quipe a de\\u0301veloppe\\u0301 un dispositif d\\u2019essai multilocal qui peut se\\r\\nre\\u0301aliser dans les champs des producteurs, et avec leur participation. L\\u2019e\\u0301valuation du\\r\\nrendement est possible et a permis l\\u2019identification de varie\\u0301te\\u0301s plus performantes. L\\u2019e\\u0301valuation par les producteurs permet simultane\\u0301ment l\\u2019identification de varie\\u0301te\\u0301s performantes\\r\\nmais aussi acceptables pour l\\u2019utilisation dans les syste\\u0300mes locaux de culture et de\\r\\nconsommation.\\r\\n<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Cette ressource a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 ajout\\u00e9e \\u00e0 cette base de donn\\u00e9es dans le cadre d\'une migration de ressource \\u00e0 partir de la plate-forme CCRP Sphaera, aujourd\'hui disparue, et attend toujours un examen complet et un contr\\u00f4le de la qualit\\u00e9.<br><\\/p><br><\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\"}',7,17,'cover_images/troves/56ba9f8b7142895af0e81e6b8ba3972c.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"http://revues.cirad.fr/index.php/cahiers-agricultures/article/view/30699\"}]}',NULL,'2008-04-01','2019-07-31 09:20:25','2019-10-23 14:54:54',NULL,NULL,'files/selection-participative-des-varietes-de-sorgho-a-laide-dessais-multilocaux-dans-deux-zones-cibles_2019-07-31_09:20:24/selection-participative-des-varietes-de-sorgho-a-laide-dessais-multilocaux-dans-deux-zones-cibles_2019-07-31_09:20:24.zip',1),(355,'{\"en\":\"Semillas de Reflexi\\u00f3n y Esperanza: Minga Para el Desarrollo Sustentable\"}','semillas-de-reflexion-y-esperanza-minga-para-el-desarrollo-sustentable_2019-07-31_09:48:58',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>Gui\\u0301a para Profesores\\/as Rurales sobre Agrobiodiversidad<br><\\/p><p>Lo que ofrece la Gui\\u0301a:<br>Esta gui\\u0301a es el resultado del trabajo participativo de docentes y te\\u0301cnicos, para proporcionar una herramienta a la educacio\\u0301n formal sobre el tema de AGROBIODIVERSIDAD, tomando en cuenta que es parte fundamental de la seguridad y soberani\\u0301a alimentaria de nuestros pueblos, pues la conservacio\\u0301n y uso de cultivos nativos con diversidad de productos es una alternativa ba\\u0301sica para garantizar el desarrollo sociocultural y econo\\u0301mico, asi\\u0301 como el rescate y uso de saberes ancestrales que hacen tradicionalmente parte de la agrobiodiversidad.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/p><div class=\\\"page\\\" title=\\\"Page 4\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"layoutArea\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"column\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>Autores: Pablo Sa\\u0301enz, Claire Nicklin y David Williams en colaboracio\\u0301n\\r\\ncon la: Asociacio\\u0301n de Educadores Ambientalistas de Cotacachi -\\r\\nASEAC\\r\\n<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>Cette ressource a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 ajout\\u00e9e \\u00e0 cette base de donn\\u00e9es dans le cadre d\'une migration de ressource \\u00e0 partir de la plate-forme CCRP Sphaera, aujourd\'hui disparue, et attend toujours un examen complet et un contr\\u00f4le de la qualit\\u00e9.<br><\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/92bee24df9644adb34032bff4b62b9cc.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[{\\\"path\\\":\\\"files\\\\/semillas-de-reflexion-y-esperanza-minga-para-el-desarrollo-sustentable_2019-07-31_09:48:58\\\\/2019-07-31_09:48:58_plan-escolar-agrobiodiversidad-cotacachi.pdf\\\",\\\"storedName\\\":\\\"2019-07-31_09:48:58_plan-escolar-agrobiodiversidad-cotacachi.pdf\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Plan_escolar_agrobiodiversidad_cotacachi.pdf\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"pdf\\\",\\\"size\\\":23184553,\\\"type_id\\\":1}]\"}','{\"en\": null}',NULL,'2009-01-01','2019-07-31 09:48:59','2019-10-23 14:55:00',NULL,NULL,'files/semillas-de-reflexion-y-esperanza-minga-para-el-desarrollo-sustentable_2019-07-31_09:48:58/semillas-de-reflexion-y-esperanza-minga-para-el-desarrollo-sustentable_2019-07-31_09:48:58.zip',1),(356,'{\"en\":\"NaRIA (Natural Resource Integrity Assessment) Score Card\"}','naria-natural-resource-integrity-assessment-score-card_2019-07-31_10:16:38',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<div class=\\\"page\\\" title=\\\"Page 3\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"section\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"layoutArea\\\">\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<div class=\\\"column\\\">A data collection sheet designed to rapidly gain an understanding of the resource conditions of farms. <\\/div><div class=\\\"column\\\">This could potentially be helpful as a good example of the design of a such sheets or forms, as it allows for quick assessment of criteria. <br><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\"><\\/span><\\/div><div class=\\\"column\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\"><br><\\/span><\\/div><div class=\\\"column\\\"><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">From the introduction:<\\/span><\\/div><div class=\\\"column\\\">The purpose of the NaRIA Score Card is to provide a rapid\\r\\nassessment of the Natural Resource Integrity (NRI) status\\r\\nof farms to be involved in experimental work in Action\\r\\nSites within Action Areas of the Humidtropics CGIAR\\r\\nResearch Program. This would allow stratification of\\r\\nstudy farms according to initial NRI status when analyzing\\r\\nresults of large numbers of participatory on-farm trials to\\r\\nbe conducted at each Action Area.\\r\\n\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>The NaRIA Score Cards are designed to be used by SRT2\\r\\nAction Site teams for NRI assessments of study farms\\r\\nat Field Sites within Action Sites. This would involve\\r\\nfarm-walks and conversations with farmers in-situ while\\r\\nmarking a square using a pencil around the colored circles\\r\\n( ) that characterize the status of indicators for different\\r\\nsections of the NaRIA Score Cards. Once assessments\\r\\nare completed by SRT2 Action Site teams, all used NaRIA\\r\\nScore Cards will be stored safely at a central location and\\r\\ncollection will be organized by the SRT2.3 focal person in\\r\\neach Action Area for further analysis.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<p>The utilization of the NaRIA score card is simple and allows\\r\\nhaving a rapid and quantitative visual estimation of NRI\\r\\nstatus for each study farm. After combining results for\\r\\nthe five indicators in each of six NRI status assessment\\r\\ndimensions (i.e. landscape context, soil erosion, soil\\r\\norganic matter content, soil nutrient availability, soil\\r\\nbiological activity, incidence of pest, weeds and diseases)\\r\\nan overall farm assessment can be generated.\\r\\n<\\/p>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\r\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/aec2538c81d4fbe18604edee1048b966.jpg',0,'{\"en\": \"[{\\\"path\\\":\\\"files\\\\/naria-natural-resource-integrity-assessment-score-card_2019-07-31_10:16:38\\\\/2019-07-31_10:16:38_naria-score-card-version-0.pdf\\\",\\\"storedName\\\":\\\"2019-07-31_10:16:38_naria-score-card-version-0.pdf\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"NaRIA SCORE CARD Version 0.pdf\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"pdf\\\",\\\"size\\\":413602,\\\"type_id\\\":1}]\"}','{\"en\": null}',NULL,NULL,'2019-07-31 10:16:39','2019-07-31 14:07:38','2019-07-31 14:07:38',NULL,'files/naria-natural-resource-integrity-assessment-score-card_2019-07-31_10:16:38/naria-natural-resource-integrity-assessment-score-card_2019-07-31_10:16:38.zip',0),(357,'{\"en\":\"Making a Shiny app that can be modified\\/updated by external people\"}','making-a-shiny-app-that-can-be-modifiedupdated-by-external-people_2019-07-31_16:25:47',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>Sometimes, you may want to have a shiny app whose data and\\/or code can be updated or mo