_tutorial.rmd\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"tutorial.rmd\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"rmd\\\",\\\"size\\\":4872,\\\"type_id\\\":1}}\"}','{\"en\": null}',NULL,'2019-07-01','2019-07-31 16:25:48','2019-07-31 16:31:16',NULL,NULL,'files/making-a-shiny-app-that-can-be-modifiedupdated-by-external-people_2019-07-31_16:25:47/making-a-shiny-app-that-can-be-modifiedupdated-by-external-people_2019-07-31_16:25:47.zip',0),(358,'{\"en\":\"A data collection monitoring shiny app\"}','a-data-collection-monitoring-shiny-app_2019-07-31_17:08:11',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>In the MESH2 project, a few of the individuals who responded to the main questionnaires were asked again some of the questions in order to check the quality of the data collection. This is the script and url of the data collection monitoring shiny app used for this purpose. The app merges the data, calculates some quality indices based on matching of the responses, and shows a summary table as well as a row data tables that can be arrenged and filtered by various variables (organisation, district, team leader, enumerator). <\\/p><p>Note: change the start date to 2019-07-01 to see some data when using the app<br><\\/p>\"}',14,19,'cover_images/troves/6f9b00aea096db5f67c6a6faa94bb46a.jpg',0,'{\"en\": \"[{\\\"path\\\":\\\"files\\\\/a-data-collection-monitoring-shiny-app_2019-07-31_17:08:11\\\\/2019-07-31_17:08:11_app.R\\\",\\\"storedName\\\":\\\"2019-07-31_17:08:11_app.R\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"app.R\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"R\\\",\\\"size\\\":13169,\\\"type_id\\\":1}]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://shiny.stats4sd.org/Mesh2/\"}]}',NULL,'2019-07-01','2019-07-31 17:08:11','2019-07-31 17:11:27',NULL,NULL,'files/a-data-collection-monitoring-shiny-app_2019-07-31_17:08:11/a-data-collection-monitoring-shiny-app_2019-07-31_17:08:11.zip',0),(359,'{\"en\":\"Managing aflatoxins in groundnuts during drying and storage\",\"fr\":\"Gestion des aflatoxines dans les arachides pendant le s\\u00e9chage et le stockage\",\"es\":\"El manejo de aflatoxinas en man\\u00ed\"}','managing-aflatoxins-in-groundnuts-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_11:28:46',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><span>A short video explaining the importance of, and methods for, managing aflatoxins in groundnuts. <\\/span><span><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in the Andes with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Found<\\/span>ation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<br><\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"<p>Une courte vid\\u00e9o expliquant l\\u2019importance de la gestion des aflatoxines dans les arachides et les m\\u00e9thodes pour la g\\u00e9rer.<br><\\/p><p>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des \\r\\nagriculteurs et des chercheurs des Andes, avec le soutien du programme \\r\\nde recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight.\\r\\n Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.<\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p>Un video corto que explica la importancia y los m\\u00e9todos para manejar las aflatoxinas en los cacahuetes.<\\/p><p>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con \\r\\nagricultores e investigadores que trabajan en los Andes con el apoyo del\\r\\n Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n \\r\\nMcKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el \\r\\nsitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.<\\/p>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/77ecffb61d6140bd8c199109aeaa6ccb.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/managing-aflatoxins-groundnuts-during-drying-and-storage\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/el-manejo-de-aflatoxinas-en-mani\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/gestion-des-aflatoxines-dans-les-arachides-pendant-le-sechage-et-le-stockage\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 11:28:47','2019-08-20 15:24:35',NULL,NULL,'files/managing-aflatoxins-in-groundnuts-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_11:28:46/managing-aflatoxins-in-groundnuts-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_11:28:46.zip',1),(360,'{\"en\":\"Growing lupin without disease\",\"es\":\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\/es\\/producir-tarwi-sin-enfermedad\",\"fr\":\"Produire du lupin sans maladie\"}','growing-lupin-without-disease_2019-08-13_11:41:41',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<span><\\/span><span><\\/span><p><span>A short video providing guidance on how to grow Lupin. <\\/span><\\/p><p><span>From the website description:<br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>\\\"Lupin can be grown in high or cold areas. Lupin is healthy food, rich in\\r\\n proteins, and good for the soil. In this video, farmers in Bolivia show\\r\\n how to keep your field free from anthracnose disease.\\\"<\\/span><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in the Andes with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Found<\\/span>ation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<br><\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p>Un video corto que brinda orientaci\\u00f3n sobre c\\u00f3mo cultivar Lupin.<br><br>De la descripci\\u00f3n del sitio web:<br><br>\\\"El lupino se puede cultivar en \\u00e1reas altas o fr\\u00edas. El lupino es un alimento saludable, rico en prote\\u00ednas y bueno para el suelo. En este video, los agricultores en Bolivia muestran c\\u00f3mo mantener su campo libre de la enfermedad de antracnosis\\\".<br><\\/p><p>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con \\r\\nagricultores e investigadores que trabajan en los Andes con el apoyo del\\r\\n Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n \\r\\nMcKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el \\r\\nsitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.<\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"<p>Une courte vid\\u00e9o expliquant comment faire pousser Lupin.<br><br>De la description du site:<br><br>\\\"Le lupin peut \\u00eatre cultiv\\u00e9 dans les r\\u00e9gions froides ou \\u00e9lev\\u00e9es. Le lupin est un aliment sain, riche en prot\\u00e9ines et bon pour le sol. Dans cette vid\\u00e9o, les agriculteurs de Bolivie montrent comment garder votre champ exempt de la maladie de l\'anthracnose.\\\"<br><\\/p><p>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des \\r\\nagriculteurs et des chercheurs des Andes, avec le soutien du programme \\r\\nde recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight.\\r\\n Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.<\\/p>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/74783bbd2edb0a62197745c507756c4b.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/growing-lupin-without-disease\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/producir-tarwi-sin-enfermedad\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/produire-du-lupin-sans-maladie\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 11:41:42','2019-08-19 11:24:46',NULL,NULL,'files/growing-lupin-without-disease_2019-08-13_11:41:41/growing-lupin-without-disease_2019-08-13_11:41:41.zip',1),(361,'{\"en\":\"Living windbreaks to protect the soil\",\"es\":\"Barreras vivas para proteger el suelo\",\"fr\":\"Des brise-vent vivants pour prot\\u00e9ger le sol\"}','living-windbreaks-to-protect-the-soil_2019-08-13_12:15:04',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<span><\\/span><p><span>A short video explaining how \'live barriers\' can be used by farmers in the Andes to protect find soil from being blown away in the strong winds.<br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>These barriers consist of native grass, bushes and trees, which are adapted to grow well in the dry, windy conditions of the area.<\\/span><\\/p><p><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in the Andes with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Found<\\/span>ation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<br><\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p>Un video corto que explica c\\u00f3mo los agricultores de los Andes pueden usar \'barreras vivas\' para proteger el suelo del viento de los fuertes vientos.<br><br>Estas barreras consisten en pasto nativo, arbustos y \\u00e1rboles, que est\\u00e1n adaptados para crecer bien en las condiciones secas y ventosas de la zona.<\\/p><p>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con \\r\\nagricultores e investigadores que trabajan en los Andes con el apoyo del\\r\\n Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n \\r\\nMcKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el \\r\\nsitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.<\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"<p>Une courte vid\\u00e9o sur l\'enregistrement des informations m\\u00e9t\\u00e9orologiques - en quoi cela peut \\u00eatre b\\u00e9n\\u00e9fique pour les agriculteurs et diff\\u00e9rentes m\\u00e9thodes de collecte de ces informations. Il comprend des entretiens avec des agriculteurs en Bolivie qui utilisent un cahier pour enregistrer et comprendre les informations m\\u00e9t\\u00e9orologiques, pr\\u00e9voir le temps et prendre des d\\u00e9cisions concernant leurs pratiques agricoles en fonction de ce qu\'ils ont d\\u00e9couvert.<\\/p><p>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des \\r\\nagriculteurs et des chercheurs des Andes, avec le soutien du programme \\r\\nde recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight.\\r\\n Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.<\\/p>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/53862ace31babc1be5ef4de60b32ecad.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/living-windbreaks-protect-soil\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/barreras-vivas-para-proteger-el-suelo\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/des-brise-vent-vivants-pour-proteger-le-sol\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 12:15:05','2019-08-20 15:24:52',NULL,NULL,'files/living-windbreaks-to-protect-the-soil_2019-08-13_12:15:04/living-windbreaks-to-protect-the-soil_2019-08-13_12:15:04.zip',1),(362,'{\"en\":\"Recording the weather\",\"fr\":\"Enregistrer les variations de la m\\u00e9t\\u00e9o\",\"es\":\"Hacer un registro del clima\"}','recording-the-weather_2019-08-13_12:28:10',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><span>A short video about recording weather information - how this can be of benefit for farmers and different methods of collecting this information. It includes interviews with farmers in Bolivia who have been using a notebook to record and understand weather information, forecast the weather and make decisions about their farming practices based on what they have found.<br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in the Andes with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Found<\\/span>ation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish,&nbsp; in the accessagriculture.org website<\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"<p>Une courte vid\\u00e9o sur l\'enregistrement des informations m\\u00e9t\\u00e9orologiques - en quoi cela peut \\u00eatre b\\u00e9n\\u00e9fique pour les agriculteurs et diff\\u00e9rentes m\\u00e9thodes de collecte de ces informations. Il comprend des entretiens avec des agriculteurs en Bolivie qui utilisent un cahier pour enregistrer et comprendre les informations m\\u00e9t\\u00e9orologiques, pr\\u00e9voir le temps et prendre des d\\u00e9cisions concernant leurs pratiques agricoles en fonction de ce qu\'ils ont d\\u00e9couvert.<\\/p><p>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des \\r\\nagriculteurs et des chercheurs des Andes, avec le soutien du programme \\r\\nde recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight.\\r\\n Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.<\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p>Un breve video sobre c\\u00f3mo registrar informaci\\u00f3n meteorol\\u00f3gica: c\\u00f3mo esto puede ser beneficioso para los agricultores y los diferentes m\\u00e9todos para recopilar esta informaci\\u00f3n. Incluye entrevistas con agricultores en Bolivia que han estado usando un cuaderno para registrar y comprender la informaci\\u00f3n meteorol\\u00f3gica, pronosticar el clima y tomar decisiones sobre sus pr\\u00e1cticas agr\\u00edcolas en funci\\u00f3n de lo que han encontrado.<\\/p><p>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con \\r\\nagricultores e investigadores que trabajan en los Andes con el apoyo del\\r\\n Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n \\r\\nMcKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el \\r\\nsitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.<\\/p>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/19246d6ed5df06efb05d4b42a62c26c5.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/recording-weather\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/hacer-un-registro-del-clima\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/enregistrer-les-variations-de-la-meteo\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 12:28:10','2019-08-21 11:20:07',NULL,NULL,'files/recording-the-weather_2019-08-13_12:28:10/recording-the-weather_2019-08-13_12:28:10.zip',1),(363,'{\"en\":\"Forecasting the weather with an app\",\"fr\":\"Pr\\u00e9dire la m\\u00e9t\\u00e9o \\u00e0 l\\u2019aide d\\u2019une application\",\"es\":\"Pronosticar el clima con una aplicaci\\u00f3n\"}','forecasting-the-weather-with-an-app_2019-08-13_12:37:59',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><span>A video about the \'Weather Underground\' app, which some farmers in Bolivia are using to get weather forecasts alongside more traditional methods of predicting weather in the short-term. <br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in the Andes with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Found<\\/span>ation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p><br><\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<br><\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"Une vid\\u00e9o sur l\'application \'Weather Underground\', que certains agriculteurs de Bolivie utilisent pour obtenir des pr\\u00e9visions m\\u00e9t\\u00e9orologiques parall\\u00e8lement aux m\\u00e9thodes plus traditionnelles de pr\\u00e9vision du temps \\u00e0 court terme.<br><br>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des agriculteurs et des chercheurs des Andes, avec le soutien du programme de recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight. Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.\",\"es\":\"Un video sobre la aplicaci\\u00f3n \'Weather Underground\', que algunos agricultores en Bolivia est\\u00e1n utilizando para obtener pron\\u00f3sticos del tiempo junto con m\\u00e9todos m\\u00e1s tradicionales para predecir el clima a corto plazo.<br><br>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con agricultores e investigadores que trabajan en los Andes con el apoyo del Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n McKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el sitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/1d071a988678b54a9e86b2e3ec0dcc28.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/forecasting-weather-app\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/pronosticar-el-clima-con-una-aplicacion\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/predire-la-meteo-laide-dune-application\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 12:37:59','2019-08-20 15:25:08',NULL,NULL,'files/forecasting-the-weather-with-an-app_2019-08-13_12:37:59/forecasting-the-weather-with-an-app_2019-08-13_12:37:59.zip',1),(364,'{\"en\":\"Killing fall armyworms naturally\",\"es\":\"Matar al cogollero de forma natural\",\"fr\":\"Tuer les chenilles l\\u00e9gionnaires d\'automne de fa\\u00e7on naturelle\"}','killing-fall-armyworms-naturally_2019-08-13_12:54:41',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><span>A video explaining methods for managing the fall armyworm without the use of chemical pesticides, and the reasons for doing so. It talks about \\\"farmers\' friends\\\" - animals that help control pests including fall armyworm.&nbsp; Farmers explain their experience and practices for pest management.<br><\\/span><\\/p><p><span>This video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in East Africa with support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Foundation. <\\/span>There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<br><\\/p>\",\"es\":\"Un video que explica los m\\u00e9todos para manejar el gusano del ej\\u00e9rcito de oto\\u00f1o sin el uso de pesticidas qu\\u00edmicos, y las razones para hacerlo. Habla de los \\\"amigos de los granjeros\\\", animales que ayudan a controlar las plagas, incluida la lombriz de oto\\u00f1o. Los agricultores explican su experiencia y pr\\u00e1cticas para el manejo de plagas.<br><br>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con agricultores e investigadores que trabajan en \\u00c1frica Oriental con el apoyo del Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n McKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en muchos idiomas en el sitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.\",\"fr\":\"Une vid\\u00e9o expliquant les m\\u00e9thodes de gestion de la chenille l\\u00e9gionnaire d\'automne sans utiliser de pesticides chimiques, et les raisons de le faire. Il parle d \'\\\"amis des agriculteurs\\\" - des animaux qui aident \\u00e0 contr\\u00f4ler les parasites, y compris le l\\u00e9gionnaire d\'automne. Les agriculteurs expliquent leur exp\\u00e9rience et leurs pratiques en mati\\u00e8re de lutte antiparasitaire.<br><br>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des agriculteurs et des chercheurs travaillant en Afrique de l\\u2019Est avec le soutien du Programme de recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight. Le site Web<a href=\\\" https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.<br>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/0cef98de30f71e712079a0d3d7744bec.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/killing-fall-armyworms-naturally\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/matar-al-cogollero-de-forma-natural\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/tuer-les-chenilles-legionnaires-dautomne-de-facon-naturelle\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 12:54:42','2019-08-20 15:25:32',NULL,NULL,'files/killing-fall-armyworms-naturally_2019-08-13_12:54:41/killing-fall-armyworms-naturally_2019-08-13_12:54:41.zip',1),(365,'{\"en\":\"Scouting for fall armyworms\",\"fr\":\"D\\u00e9pistage des chenilles l\\u00e9gionnaires d\\u2019automne\",\"es\":\"Buscando cogolleros\"}','scouting-for-fall-armyworms_2019-08-13_13:52:31',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>A video advising the practice of inspecting fields regularly in the first 6 weeks of growing crops to manage fall armyworm infestations. <br><\\/p><p>This video was produced by Agro-Insight in collaboration with \\r\\nfarmers and researchers working in East Africa with the support of the \\r\\nCollaborative Crop Research Programme of the McKnight Foundation.\\r\\nThere are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.\\r\\n<\\/p><p style=\\\"font-size:11pt;font-family:Calibri,sans-serif;margin:0;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\\\">This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<\\/span><\\/p>\",\"fr\":\"Une vid\\u00e9o conseillant d\'inspecter r\\u00e9guli\\u00e8rement les champs au cours des six premi\\u00e8res semaines de culture afin de g\\u00e9rer les infestations de l\\u00e9gionnaires d\'automne.<br><br>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des agriculteurs et des chercheurs travaillant en Afrique de l\'Est avec le soutien du Programme de recherche sur les cultures en collaboration de la Fondation McKnight. Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org \\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org <\\/a>contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.\",\"es\":\"Un video que aconseja la pr\\u00e1ctica de inspeccionar los campos regularmente durante las primeras 6 semanas de cultivo para controlar las infestaciones de gusanos del ej\\u00e9rcito de oto\\u00f1o.<br><br>Este video fue producido por Agro-Insight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con agricultores e investigadores que trabajan en \\u00c1frica Oriental con el apoyo del Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n McKnight. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el sitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/71ecf248a550016989edf3946f6be326.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/scouting-fall-armyworms\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/buscando-cogolleros\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/depistage-des-chenilles-legionnaires-dautomne\"}, []]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 13:52:31','2019-08-20 15:25:42',NULL,NULL,'files/scouting-for-fall-armyworms_2019-08-13_13:52:31/scouting-for-fall-armyworms_2019-08-13_13:52:31.zip',1),(366,'{\"en\":\"Managing aflatoxins in maize during drying and storage\",\"es\":\"Manejo de aflatoxinas en ma\\u00edz durante el secado y almacenamiento\",\"fr\":\"Gestion des aflatoxines dans le ma\\u00efs pendant le s\\u00e9chage et le stockage\"}','managing-aflatoxins-in-maize-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_16:01:42',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>A video in which farmers in Tanzania explain and demonstrate how they\\r\\n dry and store their maize in order to help manage aflatoxins. <\\/p><p>This\\r\\n video was produced by AgroInsight in collaboration with farmers and \\r\\nresearchers working in Tanzania. It was produced for the Yieldwise \\r\\nproject, funded by the Rockefeller Foundation. There are plenty more interesting videos in many languages on the website <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" rel=\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\" data-auth=\\\"NotApplicable\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a>\\r\\nand we invite you to explore it.<\\/p><p>This video is available in multiple languages, including Spanish, in the accessagriculture.org website<\\/p><p><br><\\/p>\",\"es\":\"Un video en el que los agricultores de Tanzania explican y demuestran c\\u00f3mo secan y almacenan su ma\\u00edz para ayudar a controlar las aflatoxinas.<br><br>Este video fue producido por AgroInsight en colaboraci\\u00f3n con agricultores e investigadores que trabajan en Tanzania. Fue producido para el proyecto Yieldwise, financiado por la Fundaci\\u00f3n Rockefeller. Hay muchos m\\u00e1s videos interesantes en varios idiomas en el sitio web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> y los invitamos a explorarlo.\",\"fr\":\"Une vid\\u00e9o dans laquelle des agriculteurs tanzaniens expliquent et montrent comment ils s\\u00e8chent et stockent leur ma\\u00efs afin de contribuer \\u00e0 la gestion des aflatoxines.<br><br>Cette vid\\u00e9o a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produite par AgroInsight en collaboration avec des agriculteurs et des chercheurs travaillant en Tanzanie. Il a \\u00e9t\\u00e9 produit pour le projet Yieldwise, financ\\u00e9 par la Fondation Rockefeller. Le site Web <a href=\\\"https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">https:\\/\\/www.accessagriculture.org<\\/a> contient de nombreuses autres vid\\u00e9os int\\u00e9ressantes dans de nombreuses langues et nous vous invitons \\u00e0 les explorer.\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/fe3ffe1c326d6ce6fc02b54f17ed0451.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\", \"fr\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/managing-aflatoxins-maize-during-drying-and-storage\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/es/manejo-de-aflatoxinas-en-maiz-durante-el-secado-y-almacenamiento\"}], \"fr\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.accessagriculture.org/fr/gestion-des-aflatoxines-dans-le-mais-pendant-le-sechage-et-le-stockage\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-13 16:01:43','2019-08-20 15:25:47',NULL,NULL,'files/managing-aflatoxins-in-maize-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_16:01:42/managing-aflatoxins-in-maize-during-drying-and-storage_2019-08-13_16:01:42.zip',1),(367,'{\"en\":\"Beyond average: new approaches to understand heterogeneity and risk of technology success or failure in smallholder farming\",\"es\":\"M\\u00e1sall\\u00e1 De Los Promedios: Nuevos Enfoques Para Entender La Heterogeneidady El Riesgo Del \\u00c9xito O Fracaso De La Tecnolog\\u00eda En Los Sistemas Agr\\u00edcolasde Peque\\u00f1os Productores\"}','beyond-average-new-approaches-to-understand-heterogeneity-and-risk-of-technology-success-or-failure-in-smallholder-farming_2019-08-13_16:19:53',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Abstract:<\\/span><\\/p><p>In recent years, many studies have demonstrated the heterogeneity of the\\r\\n smallholder production environment. Yet agronomic research for \\r\\ndevelopment (R4D) that aims to identify and test options for increasing \\r\\nproductivity has not consistently adapted its approaches to such \\r\\nheterogeneous conditions. This paper describes the challenges facing \\r\\nresearch, highlighting the importance of variation in evaluating the \\r\\nperformance of soil management recommendations, integrating aspects of \\r\\nproduction risk management within the formulation of recommendations, \\r\\nand proposing alternative approaches to implement agronomic R4D. \\r\\nApproaches are illustrated using two multi-locational on-farm paired \\r\\ntrials, each having one no-input control treatment and a treatment with \\r\\nfertilizer application for maize in Western Kenya and for beans in \\r\\nEastern Rwanda. The diversity of treatment responses should be embraced \\r\\nrather than avoided to gain a better understanding of current context \\r\\nand its relation with past management.<\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Resumen:<\\/span><\\/p><p>En los \\u00faltimos a\\u00f1os, muchos estudios han demostrado la heterogeneidad del entorno de producci\\u00f3nde los peque\\u00f1os  agricultores. Sin  embargo,  la  investigaci\\u00f3n  agron\\u00f3mica  para  el  desarrollo  (R4D),  cuyo  objetivo  es identificar  y  probar  opciones  para  aumentar  la  productividad,  no  ha  adaptado consistentemente sus enfoques a estas condiciones de heterogeneidad. En este  art\\u00edculo sedescribenlos desaf\\u00edos que enfrenta la investigaci\\u00f3n, destacandola    importancia    de    la    variaci\\u00f3n    al    evaluar    la    implementaci\\u00f3n    de    las recomendaciones  para  el  manejo  delsuelo, integrando dentro  de  la  formulaci\\u00f3n  de  recomendaciones los aspectos de la gesti\\u00f3n de riesgos en la producci\\u00f3ny proponiendo enfoques alternativos para implementar la investigaci\\u00f3n  agron\\u00f3mica  para  el  desarrollo  (R4D). Para  ilustrar  los  enfoques  se  utilizan dos pruebaspareadasmultilocalizadas realizadas en finca. Cada una de ellas tiene un tratamiento de control sin insumosy un tratamiento con aplicaci\\u00f3n de fertilizante para el ma\\u00edz en el oestede Kenia y para el fr\\u00edjol en el estede Ruanda. La diversidad de respuestas al tratamiento deber\\u00eda acogerse,en lugarde evitarse, para as\\u00ed entender mejor el contextoactual y su relaci\\u00f3n con la gesti\\u00f3nanterior.<\\/p>\"}',7,17,'cover_images/troves/674bd2d08bf3304d32611bab26a5fb47.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/303720245_Beyond_average_new_approaches_to_understand_heterogeneity_and_risk_of_technology_success_or_failure_in_smallholder_farming\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"http://www.andescdp.org/sites/default/files/docuemntos_relevantes/Vanlauwe_Coe_Mas_alla_de_promedios_2.pdf\"}]}',NULL,'2016-05-01','2019-08-13 16:19:54','2019-08-20 15:26:08',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(368,'{\"en\":\"Como usar Zotero\"}','como-usar-zotero_2019-08-14_09:34:59',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>En este video, se explica c\\u00f3mo usar Zotero para administrar la revision bibiogr\\u00e1fica en un proceso de investigaci\\u00f3n.&nbsp;<\\/p><p>No estamos promoviendo el uso de Zotero, pero dada la frecuencia de uso que encontramos de este software y la necesidad de usar sistemas de manejo de citas, incluimos este video como ejemplo. Otras herramientas similares tambi\\u00e9n estan disponibles.<\\/p>\"}',7,16,'cover_images/troves/cbe991758b30678a056706e57f715d8e.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": null}',NULL,'2019-04-01','2019-08-14 09:34:59','2019-08-19 10:56:53',NULL,'FEkSiqXP7tg',NULL,1),(369,'{\"en\":\"CCRP Integrated Monitoring,  Evaluation, and Planning (IMEP) Handbook\",\"es\":\"Gu\\u00eda de Monitoreo, Evaluacion y Planificacion Integrado (MEPI) para la CCRP\"}','guia-de-monitoreo-evaluacion-y-planificacion-integrado-mepi-para-la-ccrp_2019-08-14_09:53:56',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p><\\/p><p>A guide for monitoring and evaluation of research projects and development funded by the McKnight Foundation Collaborative Crop Research Program<span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\"><br><\\/span><\\/p><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Introduction to the Guide:<\\/span><p><\\/p><p>This guide is intended to orient project, regional,and program teams to the integrated monitoring, evaluation, and planning (IMEP) process of the Collaborative Crop Research Program (CCRP) at The McKnight Foundation. This framework is used to guide the program\'s strategies for grantmaking, grantee support, and shared learning at the project, regional,and program levels. For more information, see the<a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ccrp.org\\/program-essentials\\/theory-change\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> CCRP Theory of Change<\\/a>.<\\/p><p>The guide:<\\/p><ul><li>defines integrated monitoring, evaluation, and planning in the CCRP<\\/li><li>explains the theory behind the approach, and <br><\\/li><li>outlines how project, regional,and program teams use IMEP, including the documents that project teams produce as part of the grant implementation process.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>This document is one of many CCRP resources available to support project and regional teams in working efficiently and effectively. For other resources see: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ccrp.org\\/how-we-work\\/imep\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">http:\\/\\/ccrp.org\\/how-we-work\\/imep<\\/a><\\/p>\",\"es\":\"<p>Una gu\\u00eda para el monitoreo y evaluaci\\u00f3n de proyectos de investigaci\\u00f3n y desarrollo financiados por el Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos de la Fundaci\\u00f3n McKnight<br><br><span style=\\\"font-weight: bold;\\\">Introducci\\u00f3n a la Gu\\u00eda<\\/span><br><br>El prop\\u00f3sito de esta gu\\u00eda es orientara los equipos de los proyectos, regionales y de programas en el proceso de monitoreo, evaluaci\\u00f3n y planificaci\\u00f3n integral (MEPI) del Programa Colaborativo de Investigaci\\u00f3n de Cultivos (CCRP) de la Fundaci\\u00f3n McKnight. Este marco se utiliza para orientar las estrategias del programa en cuanto a concesi\\u00f3n de subvenciones, apoyo a beneficiarios de subvenciones, y socializaci\\u00f3n de los aprendizajes a nivel de proyectos, regionales y de programas.<br><br>La gu\\u00eda:<\\/p><ul><li>definelos procesos integrados de monitoreo, evaluaci\\u00f3n y planificaci\\u00f3n en e lCCRP<\\/li><li>explica la teor\\u00eda que respalda el enfoque, y<\\/li><li>describela forma como los equipos de los proyectos, regionales y de programas utilizan el MEPI, incluyendo los documentos producidos por los equipos del proyecto como parte del proceso de implementaci\\u00f3n de la subvenci\\u00f3n.<\\/li><\\/ul><p>Este documento es uno de los muchos recursos que el CCRP pone a disposici\\u00f3n de los equipos de los proyectos y regionales para contribuir a la eficiencia y efectividad de su trabajo.Para ver otros recursos consulte: <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/ccrp.org\\/how-we-work\\/imep\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">http:\\/\\/ccrp.org\\/how-we-work\\/imep<\\/a><\\/p>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/78799672cfb1a33c623b23551ac1a715.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"http://www.ccrp.org/sites/default/files/imep_manual_15_feb_17.pdf\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"http://www.andescdp.oarg/sites/default/files/docuemntos_relevantes/Guia_MEPI_v2.pdf\"}]}',NULL,'2017-02-01','2019-08-14 09:53:56','2019-08-20 15:30:41',NULL,NULL,'files/guia-de-monitoreo-evaluacion-y-planificacion-integrado-mepi-para-la-ccrp_2019-08-14_09:53:56/guia-de-monitoreo-evaluacion-y-planificacion-integrado-mepi-para-la-ccrp_2019-08-14_09:53:56.zip',1),(370,'{\"en\":\"Social Science Research Methods and Approaches for Research and Development Work with Farmers\",\"es\":\"Gu\\u00eda de m\\u00e9todos de investigaci\\u00f3n y enfoques de las ciencias sociales para el trabajo de investigaci\\u00f3n y desarrollo con agricultor\"}','guia-de-metodos-de-investigacion-y-enfoques-de-las-ciencias-socialespara-el-trabajo-de-investigacion-y-desarrollo-con-agricultor_2019-08-14_10:23:50',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>A guide to research methods produced by CCRP for thesis students and researchers with training in biological sciences.<\\/p><p>From the introduction:<br><\\/p><p>\\\"The    guide    is    a    quick    and    practical    introduction    to    the    methods    used    by    social    scientists    and    to    the    norms    that    allow    these    methods    to    be    used    properly    and    efficiently.    It    is    hoped    that    the    correct    use    of    these    methods    will    strengthen    the    research    and    practice    of    agronomists    and    other    biological    sciences    specialists    in    order    to    provide    solid    evidence    to    the    global    community    as    well    as    opportunities    for    learning    and    improvement    toimmediate    stakeholders    and    beneficiaries.\\\"<\\/p>\",\"es\":\"Una gu\\u00eda de m\\u00e9todos de investigaci\\u00f3n producida por CCRP para estudiantes de tesis e investigadores con formaci\\u00f3n en ciencias biol\\u00f3gicas.<br><br>\\\"La gu\\u00eda es una introducci\\u00f3n r\\u00e1pida y pr\\u00e1ctica a los m\\u00e9todos que usan cient\\u00edficos sociales y a las normas que hacen que esos m\\u00e9todos sean usados adecuada y eficientemente. Se espera que el uso correcto de estos m\\u00e9todos fortalezca la investigaci\\u00f3n y la pr\\u00e1ctica de ingenieros agr\\u00f3nomos y otros especialistas en ciencias biol\\u00f3gicas para proporcionar evidencia s\\u00f3lida a la comunidad global as\\u00ed como oportunidades de aprendizaje y mejora a las partes interesadas inmediatas y a los beneficiarios. Los objetivos finales son la mejora de la producci\\u00f3n de alimentos, la seguridad del sustento y el manejo sostenible de los recursos naturales, incluyendo la biodiversidad, todo en un contexto de equidad, y el uso apropiado de m\\u00e9todos de ciencias sociales pueden contribuir a alcanzar estos objetivos.\\\"<br>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/0bb5ce187d853e0e9794b7da7fcd56fa.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\", \"es\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"https://www.ccrp.org/resources/social-science-methods-for-agronomist-handbook/\"}], \"es\": [{\"path\": \"www.andescdp.org/sites/default/files/docuemntos_relevantes/Metodos_investigacion_CS_2014.pdf\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-14 10:23:50','2019-10-24 09:10:20',NULL,NULL,NULL,1),(371,'{\"en\":\"Gu\\u00eda para protocolos (dise\\u00f1os) e informes de investigaci\\u00f3n\"}','guia-para-protocolos-disenos-e-informes-de-investigacion_2019-08-14_10:53:46',NULL,'{\"en\":\"<p>Una gu\\u00eda de CCRP.<\\/p><p>Este documento proporciona una serie de indicaciones para guiarlo a trav\\u00e9s de la redacci\\u00f3n de protocolos e informes de investigaci\\u00f3n.<\\/p>\"}',7,13,'cover_images/troves/af429bc81b08a7e642c67f4ca3f9f7ba.jpg',1,'{\"en\": \"[]\"}','{\"en\": [{\"path\": \"http://www.andescdp.org/sites/default/files/docuemntos_relevantes/Guia_para_Protocolos_e_Informe.pdf\"}]}',NULL,NULL,'2019-08-14 10:53:46','2019-08-19 10:45:19',NULL,NULL,'files/guia-para-protocolos-disenos-e-informes-de-investigacion_2019-08-14_10:53:46/guia-para-protocolos-disenos-e-informes-de-investigacion_2019-08-14_10:53:46.zip',1),(372,'{\"en\":\"Lista de verificaci\\u00f3n de monitoreo de calidad para investigaci\\u00f3n\"}','lista-de-verificacion-de-monitoreo-de-calidad-para-investigacion_2019-08-14_11:04:49',NULL,'{\"en\":\"Esta lista de verificaci\\u00f3n de monitoreo es una herramienta de presentaci\\u00f3n de informes que tiene 