nisation; coordinating volunteer programmes in Honduras, alongside her studies. Ciara looks forward to combining her passions for development, data and mathematics at Stats4SD','Ciara joined Stats4SD in October 2019 as a Statistics Intern. She has a BSc in Actuarial Mathematics and internship experience in data analytics. During her time at Dublin City University, Ciara was involved with a non-profit health and sustainable development organisation; coordinating volunteer programmes in Honduras, alongside her studies. Ciara looks forward to combining her passions for development, data and mathematics at Stats4SD','{\"github\": null, \"twitter\": null, \"facebook\": null, \"linkedin\": null}','UK','staff_avatars/22ff1057efbf97e8cb5728af90afb882.png',NULL,32,33,1,NULL,NULL,NULL),(28,'Claire Nicklin','cnicklin@andescdp.org',NULL,NULL,'2019-11-12 16:24:31','2019-11-12 16:24:31',NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"github\": null, \"twitter\": null, \"facebook\": null, \"linkedin\": null}',NULL,NULL,0,0,0,0,NULL,NULL,NULL);
